text: Ueli Scheidegger (born 23 July 1938) is a Swiss ski jumper. He competed in the normal hill and large hill events at the 1964 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1938 births Category:Living people Category:Swiss male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Switzerland Category:Ski jumpers at the 1964 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
